notes:
### MiniScale®
* Data type: Raster
* Supply format: TIFF [LZW]
* Great Britain [304 MB]

### 1:250 000 Scale Colour Raster
* Data type: Raster
* Supply format: TIFF [LZW]
* Great Britain [112 MB]

### OS Street View®
* Data type: Raster
* Supply format: TIFF [LZW]
* Great Britain, England, Scotland, Wales
* National Grid Reference squares [1 MB - 1.2 GB]

### Boundary-Line™
* Data type: Vector
* Supply format: ESRI ® Shape
* Great Britain [250 MB]

### Code-Point® Open
* Data type: Point Data
* Supply format: CSV
* Great Britain [20 MB]

### 1:50 000 Scale Gazetteer
* Data type: Point Data
* Supply format: CSV
* Great Britain [11 MB]

### Strategi®
* Data type: Vector
* Great Britain
* [ESRI ® Shape: 52 MB]
* [DXF: 52 MB]
	
### Meridian™2
* Data type:Vector
* Great Britain
* [ESRI ® Shape: 201 MB]
* [DXF: 151 MB]

### OS Locator™
* Data type: Point Data
* Supply format: ASCII text, colon separated
* Great Britain [35 MB]

### Land-Form PANORAMA®
* Data type: Vector
* Supply format: DXF (Contours)
* Great Britain [375 MB]

### Linked Data
* See package:ordnance-survey-linked-data
